verbose_text: Furuta et al. have shown that Supartz FX induced the gene expression of dual-specificity phosphatase (DUSP) 10/mitogen activated protein kinase phosphatase (MKP) 5 MAP kinase phosphatase that dephosphorylates JNK and p38, and inactivated activated protein (AP) -1 transcription factor.
evidence: phosphatase that dephosphorylates JNK and p38
